    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/0f81c2454b3b9fced88f6481ad8ef452.poster.avif?t=1748535456\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/0f81c2454b3b9fced88f6481ad8ef452.webm?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/0f81c2454b3b9fced88f6481ad8ef452.mp4?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>世界陷入了永恒的黑暗中，只有你才能带来黎明。</i></h2><br><br>加入人类的最后一道防线 - 光之旅团，并在随机生成的战场中进行多场解救堕落灵魂之旅。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/c9532eb339c72df04456f3ad2d239d93.poster.avif?t=1748535456\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/c9532eb339c72df04456f3ad2d239d93.webm?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/c9532eb339c72df04456f3ad2d239d93.mp4?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>✧ 在紧张刺激又写实的枪战</strong>中对抗难度逐渐提升的敌方士兵。战斗系统皆以写实为基础来设计，使用使用栓动式步枪、机关枪和手枪来瞄准、射击与重新装填，让您身历其境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/5630fece7c4e2eedcd1d74805b7a620c.poster.avif?t=1748535456\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/5630fece7c4e2eedcd1d74805b7a620c.webm?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/5630fece7c4e2eedcd1d74805b7a620c.mp4?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>✧ 以程式随机生成战场的战术Roguelike玩法</strong>让每次行动都完全独一无二。敌方士兵将埋伏在各个角落，因此自身位置和作战策略都对生存至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.poster.avif?t=1748535456\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.webm?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.mp4?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>✧ 强大的光之魔法</strong>与枪战的完美融合。从伤害加成至眩晕敌人等特殊效果，各式各样的魔法都将为您的军械库增添更多有利的战斗工具。<br><br><strong>✧ 提升光之旅团的阶级</strong>以解锁新的枪支、附加零件、被动能力与各类法术。营救盟友以解锁更多可游玩的兵种职业，为你的行动增添更为丰富的多样性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.poster.avif?t=1748535456\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.webm?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.mp4?t=1748535456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>✧ 在您奋战拯救世界</strong>的过程中，逐渐揭开导致世界衰亡的谜团。",
